data.description: All Ages Welcome here at the Country View Collections Neighborhood, NO age restrictions! Two recent comps in the community were 825k (remodeled) and 798k (not remodeled), both with 55 + age restrictions. *Remodel just completed at this private ground floor single level 2/2 condominium with sweeping views of the eucalyptus canyon and sunrise skies off the nicely appointed, and very private, back patio. In addition, the welcoming front patio offers a cozy retreat for enjoying a beverage, having a conversation or reading a book. Resort atmosphere in the Country Views Collections community, with 9 hole executive course which is free to owners who can have 3 guests accompany them. Two pools, spa, pickle ball, and lots of community activities every month. Masterbedroom  has an ensuite bath and beautiful view of the canyon. Private 1 car garage
